data.description: Open ranch style floor plan with vaulted ceilings!  Concrete RV parking with double gates! The kitchen is open with gorgeous wood glazed cabinetry with double breakfast bars, stainless steel appliances, double ovens, don’t miss the walk-in pantry! Large dining room with tile floors, chandelier, and plant shelf.   Master bedroom has walk-in closet, ceiling fan, attached bathroom with double vanity, built-in cabinetry, deep soaker tub and tile surround shower! Basement is fully finished with new carpet!,Wide staircase takes you to large open family room, theater room, finished storage/ utility room, bonus open room great for office or gaming room, ¾ bathroom with new vanity, glass shower doors, and 4th and 5th bedroom. Landscaped front and backyard! Fully fence – all vinyl, auto sprinkler system, concrete curbing, back patio, raised garden bed and 2 storage sheds (included)! The laundry room is off the garage and has matching wood cabinetry.  Garage is Sheetrocked and painted, 2nd stall is extra deep, window in garage for extra light, insulated garage door, peg board, workbench and cabinetry included.  No back neighbors! Desirable neighborhood –great location by all the new schools and Rec Center!  This is a must see!
